{"tid":2198331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"15人被指操控壹傳媒股價　今全部獲准保釋","createTime":"2020-09-11T09:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T13:19:55.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"463b6e42b9059a116d3c0534a14af52fcc447eac","tid":2198331,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200911/s00001/dc27e461f91612e08a4647465b7d6df9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200911%2Fs00001%2Fdc27e461f91612e08a4647465b7d6df9.jpg&h=20869080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200911/s00001/1599815573685/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200911%2Fs00001%2F1599815573685%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4eac1d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200911%2Fs00001%2F1599815573685%2F&h=94915244\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200911/s00001/1599815573685/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方毒品調查科昨日（10日）以串謀欺詐及洗黑錢罪名拘捕15人，指控他們透過WhatsApp溝通，3日內透過9間證券行密集式交易壹傳媒股票，合共買賣逾13,200次，涉嫌製造虛假的交投量，營造交投熾熱假象，利用社交媒體的言論「引散戶入局」，並在「高位散貨」獲利，共賺逾3870萬元。<br />\n<br />\n至今午（11日）5時許，警方表示所有被捕人已獲准保釋，須於10月中旬報到。"},{"pid":"3c7297509870cb8c2cbca920b25c1647d70aca19","tid":2198331,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc963c17cd5a44a789007f134c965978784cdb27","tid":2198331,"uid